  PreLevelDialogue:
  - Words getting out kid! The SAMURAI SCULPTORS are on the prowl!
  - "They all want a piece of us! You would not believe who I just had on the phone!
    I\u2019ll give you a hint, you won't know them. THEY ARE THAT RICH!"
  - "Mhm mhm, okay fine they\u2019re just another well off family\u2026 BUT THE POINT
    STANDS!"
  - "Business is business at the end of the day right? If we\u2019re getting paid,
    I\u2019m happy."
  - "Okay anyway, progress is progress, we\u2019ll get to the big dawgs soon enough,
    and they will KNOW our name."
  - "We\u2019ll get so big they start calling us the big dawgs! We\u2019ll be winning
    so much you\u2019re gonna get SICK of winning!!"
  - Too far?
